metadata.name: Valentine's Day in Manchester
metadata.description:
Out and about in Manchester for Valentine's day with a Pentax loaded with HP5 film, this collection of 8 black and white photos, celebrates the day-to-day hustle and bustle of the busy Northern UK City. 

With a keen interest in street life, architecture and graffiti, I captured the sentiments of the city, on a grey, damp afternoon.
